FT  03 JUL 92 / World Trade News: Turkey to seek Arab financing
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
   By JOHN MURRAY BROWN
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
Turkey is to seek Arab finance to establish a regional development bank to
service the Black Sea and Central Asian states after last week's framework
economic agreement signed in Istanbul, writes John Murray Brown. Turkish
officials are to visit Jeddah today to sign an agreement with the Islamic
Development Bank.
