The decline from the comparable Pounds 26,658 reflected a 'dull trading
climate' and conditions remained 'unpredictable' directors said.
Turnover fell 8.8 per cent to Pounds 340,045 (Pounds 372,882). Earnings per
share emerged at 8.1p (18.55p).
