   By GARY MEAD, Marketing Correspondent
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
GOLD GREENLEES Trott, the advertising and marketing services group, reported
pre-tax profits down by 19 per cent, from Pounds 5.02m to Pounds 4.09m, on
