FT  03 JUL 92 / UK Company News: Northern Electric surges to Pounds 98.2m
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
   By JULIET SYCHRAVA
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
NORTHERN ELECTRIC, the Newcastle-based regional electricity company,
announced a pre-tax profit of Pounds 98.2m for the year to end-March 1992, a
