chief executive of Unigate, a company under half Northern's size, gets paid.
There's also quite a difference in the two companies' share prices over the
past year - Northern has outperformed Unigate two and a half times.
So perhaps Northern's seven shirt-sleeved directors, as pictured in the
annual report, should be allowed to celebrate with something a little
stronger than water and only five glasses.
